Class JNamedMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.modello.plugin.java.javasource.JNamedMap

  • public class JNamedMap
extends Object
    A simple String to Object mapping which preserves order.
    Note: This class is not synchronized. So be careful. :-)
    Author:
    Keith Visco
